high_descs: Pick up the bread on the table.
Go to the microwave on your left.
Put the bread in the microwave, turn it on and take it out.
Turn and and leave the room and go to the coffeetable on your right.
Put the bread on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Warm up the bread in the microwave and put it on the coffee table.

high_descs: Walk to the diningtable in front.
Pick up the bread from the table.
Turn left to reach the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and exit the dining room to walk to the coffeetable on the right.
Put the bread on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the hot bread on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Take the bread from the dining table.
Turn left, move up to fridge, take right towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the bread inside, close it, turn on, wait, turn off, open the microwave, get back the bread, close the microwave.
Turn right, move, take left, move, turn right, move forward, leave the room, walk straight, turn right towards the coffee table.
Put the bread on the top corner of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: To get the bread from dining table, heat it in the microwave, put it on the coffee table.
